comments:
Created 1.4.1935 out of the parish of Amington & Stoneydelph. 
    Abolished 1.4.1965 and added to the parish of Tamworth. See also Table 
    2, note (g).

Abolished 1.4.1935 and divided between the parishes of Amington 
    and Wilnecote & Castle Liberty. See also Table 2, note (c).

Renamed 13.11.1957 to become the parish of Glascote. See also 
    Table 2, note (c).

Created 13.11.1957 by renaming the parish of Bolehall & Glascote. 
    Abolished 1.4.1965 and added to the parish of Tamworth. See also Table 
    2, note (g).
Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the Birmingham unparished area. See also Table 2, notes (a) to (d) and (i) to (p).

Abolished 1.4.1965 and divided between the parishes of Tamworth, 
    Kingsbury, Polesowrth and Shuttington. See also Table 2, notes (c), (e) and 
    (g).
